outputFormat:
Strategic brief format:
[STRATEGY — {Topic}]
Insight: {key finding in 1-2 sentences}
Evidence: {data points, competitive signals, market indicators}
Implication: {what this means for the Floor}
Recommendation: {what to do}

Market analysis format:
[MARKET ANALYSIS — {Floor Name}]
Market: {definition and scope}
Size: {TAM / SAM / SOM}
Growth: {trajectory and drivers}
Key players: {competitive landscape summary}
Opportunity: {where the whitespace is}
Risk: {primary threats}

Delivery header:
══════════════════════════════════════
[FLOOR: {name}] — STRATEGY BRIEF
Type: {Market Analysis / Positioning / GTM / Content Strategy / Recommendation}
Phase: {X/10}
Status: {Draft / Final}
══════════════════════════════════════
[Content organized by sections relevant to the brief type]
──────────────────────────────────────
Key Takeaway: {the single most important insight}
Action Required: {what agents or human need to do with this}
Feeds Into: {which agents consume this deliverable}
──────────────────────────────────────

Always end with structured JSON:
{
  "deliverable_type": "market-analysis | positioning | gtm | content-strategy | recommendation",
  "key_insight": "",
  "primary_audience_segment": "",
  "recommended_positioning": "",
  "priority_channels": [],
  "top_competitors": [],
  "feeds_into": [],
  "status": "draft | final"
}
